  "id": "did:web:etzhayyim.com:actor:ake",
  "name": "ake",
  "displayName": "朱 — Community-Edit Membrane (Wikipedia-stance)",
  "displayNameJa": "朱",
  "displayNameEn": "Ake",
  "description": "Community-edit membrane — the Wikipedia collaborative-correction STANCE fitted to the charter. 朱 (vermillion editorial ink; 朱を入れる = to make corrections) is how a 信者 (SBT holder) proposes a correction to a KG fact or an actor profile. Every edit is a member-signed proposal appended to the kotoba Datom log (never an overwrite — 非終末論, full revision history). A Murakumo-only LLM scores risk + quality and ROUTES (the Wikipedia ORES analogue) but NEVER decides accept/reject (G2); low-risk well-sourced edits auto-accept (optimistic fast-path), risky/contested edits escalate to 1 SBT = 1 vote, and invariant-adjacent edits escalate to Council Lv7+. Mirror entity-actors are CORRECTED as observations, never spoken-as (ADR-2606042330 preserved). This is NOT anonymous open-edit: it is 信者-gated + member-signed (no-server-key) by construction (N1). ZERO invariant amendments — it STRENGTHENS no-server-key, kotoba-canonical-state, 1 SBT = 1 vote, and the mirror invariant. Per ADR-2606052100.",
  "descriptionJa": "コミュニティ編集 membrane — Wikipedia の協働訂正 STANCE を charter に適合させたもの。朱(訂正の朱墨、朱を入れる=校正)は 信者(SBT 保持者)が KG fact や actor profile の訂正を提案する仕組み。各編集は member 署名の提案として kotoba Datom log に append(上書きなし — 非終末論、完全な版履歴)。Murakumo-only LLM が risk + quality を採点し ROUTE する(Wikipedia ORES 相当)が、accept/reject は決して決めない(G2、非裁定); low-risk で出典確かな編集は optimistic 即時採用、risky/係争中は 1 SBT = 1 vote、不変条項に隣接する編集は Council Lv7+ へ escalate。ミラー entity-actor は観測として訂正でき、本人として発信は不可(ADR-2606042330 保持)。匿名オープン編集ではない: 構造的に 信者-gated + member署名(no-server-key)(N1)。invariant 改正ゼロ — no-server-key / kotoba-canonical-state / 1 SBT = 1 vote / mirror invariant をすべて強化する方向。Per ADR-2606052100。",
  "adr": {
    "master": "etzhayyim:adr:2606052100",
    "mirrorSibling": "etzhayyim:adr:2606042330",
    "noServerKey": "etzhayyim:adr:2605231525",
    "datomCanonical": "etzhayyim:adr:2605312345",
