  "tier": "Tier-B",
  "scope": {
    "phase": "R0 — ontology + 6 lexicons + 5 cells (ALL coded state machines: propose/edit_triage/review_vote/promote/revision_log; all .solve() RuntimeError at R0) + triage engine (methods/triage.py — risk + quality scoring + the PURE-FUNCTION router route_for, the G2 anchor: the model scores, it never decides) + append-only revision-history engine (methods/revision.py — append/as-of/current/history_of + non-destructive :representative→:authoritative promotion + revert = Wikipedia rollback for upheld :challenge edit-wars, restores predecessor by appending, never deletes) + contributor-trajectory engine (methods/contributor.py — G9 anti-vandalism rate limit + RECOVERABLE Wellbecoming acceptance trajectory, not a score-of-soul) + end-to-end membrane (methods/analyze.py — propose→triage→route→[optimistic|sbt-vote|council-lv7|refused]→append over the :representative seed) + genesis-revision bridge over the REAL actor-profile SSoT (methods/ingest.py — bootstraps the append-only 'view history' from the actual committed actor-profile-seed.kotoba.edn the DID-web Worker publishes from; surfaced + closed an INFRA_ACTORS↔profile-seed drift, adding mitooshi+noroshi) + :representative seed (5 edits, one per route) + one-command runner. Registered in INFRA_ACTORS → did:web:etzhayyim.com:actor:ake. 110 tests green (17 triage + 7 revision + 6 edit-war + 8 contributor + 8 ingest [HERMETIC over a committed fixture + soft real-SSoT validation] + 16 charter-invariants + 6 analyze + 5 lexicons + 10 consistency/SSoT-drift-lock + 20 cell-unit + 7 cell-chain membrane-flow integration [propose→edit_triage→review_vote→promote→revision_log threaded through the real cell state machines]). The whole suite is HERMETIC — green in any checkout, independent of whether the shared actor-profile-seed has yet been coordinated-committed with ake's record (data/sample-profile-seed.kotoba.edn fixture; real-SSoT checks are soft). Design + offline routing/revision only; NO live ingest / vote / promotion / publish.",
    "scopeBoundary": "Member-signed, LLM-triaged, vote-promoted correction of KG facts + actor profiles, with append-only revision history (design-only)",
    "exclusions": [
      "anonymous open-edit — 信者-gated + member-signed by construction (N1, G1)",
      "LLM accept/reject — the model scores+routes, never decides (N2, G2)",
      "impersonation / speak-as-entity — mirror corrected as observation only (N3, G3)",
      "overwrite / deletion of history — append-only (N4, G5)",
      "unsourced edits (N5, G4)",
      "server-signed edits / platform-held key (N6, G1/no-server-key)",
      "adjudication of legal/criminal truth (N7 — danjo/chigiri boundary)",
      "live ingest / binding vote / promotion / publish (G8 — Council Lv6+ + operator; invariant-adjacent Lv7+)"
    ]
  },
